<p>Once you have signed up for <%= SITE_NAME %> and registered for a class, the next step is 
  accessing class assignments.</p>
  <p>There are two ways to access assignments:</p>
 
  <b>1. Email notifications</b>. When an assignment becomes available, <%= SITE_NAME %> will send 
    the link to your confirmed email address. (Not receiving notifications? Go here.)</li>
  <p>  
  <b>2. OpenStax Tutor Dashboard</b>. Access the assignment via the Dashboard, per the below steps: 
  <p>
    <ol>
      <li>Click the <strong>Dashboard</strong> link.
        <%= image_tag("dashboard.png", {:border => 1, :width => "100%", 
          :height => "100%", :title=>"dashboard"})%>  
      <li>Click <strong>Class name</strong> you are taking.</li>
      <%= image_tag("classname.png", {:border => 1, :width => "100%", 
        :height => "100%", :title=>"class name"})%>
      <li>On the Class Information page, click the <strong>assignment link</strong>.</li>
      <%= image_tag("assignment_link.png", {:border => 1, :width => "100%", 
        :height => "100%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </ol>
